331
00:15:24,530 --> 00:15:27,960
♪As if trying to hide this farewell♪

332
00:15:28,350 --> 00:15:31,770
♪Yet the pain feels so real♪

333
00:15:31,910 --> 00:15:35,080
♪Growing sharper in the snow♪

334
00:15:35,240 --> 00:15:38,760
♪Snow falls across the city,
filling my heart♪

335
00:15:38,760 --> 00:15:42,740
♪The cold wind blows
through a lonely corner♪

336
00:15:43,080 --> 00:15:46,210
♪Jade fragments drift
in the wandering snow♪

337
00:15:46,210 --> 00:15:49,190
♪My heart sinks
into the vast frozen river♪

338
00:15:49,480 --> 00:15:53,240
♪Time wears on
as snow falls again and again♪

339
00:15:53,240 --> 00:15:56,600
♪Just like your endless heartlessness♪

340
00:15:56,840 --> 00:16:00,210
♪Frosted branches shake off stardust♪

341
00:16:00,390 --> 00:16:03,490
♪It's my endless devotion to you♪

342
00:16:03,780 --> 00:16:07,140
♪Snow falls across the city,
filling my heart♪

343
00:16:07,350 --> 00:16:10,590
♪That pure white is an endless longing♪

344
00:16:10,590 --> 00:16:14,240
♪The wind can't scatter the snow
it piles into a cocoon♪

345
00:16:14,450 --> 00:16:17,780
♪Trapping me in this winter♪

346
00:16:17,960 --> 00:16:21,330
♪Snow fills the city,
drifting toward the horizon♪

347
00:16:21,580 --> 00:16:25,140
♪Carrying away the sorrow of farewells♪

348
00:16:25,380 --> 00:16:28,970
♪I linger alone in the snow♪

349
00:16:28,970 --> 00:16:33,200
♪Waiting for a fate
that will never come♪
